==================================================
ASSUMPTIONS
==================================================

- User must run `go mod tidy` in each module after cloning (deps
  downloaded on first build).
- Docker Compose must be running for PostgreSQL to be reachable.
- seed_problems.sql must be run before testing suggest/list endpoints.
- In-process mock evaluator is intentionally not concurrent-safe across
  multiple simultaneous submissions (single-user MVP assumption).
